# Getting Started

If you are using Platform Automation Toolkit for the first time,
you have a few options.

See [Overview](./index.html) of Platform Automation Toolkit for a conceptual description.
Consider reviewing this before diving into more technical content.

## How-to Guides

We have in-depth procedures for deploying a new Ops Manager and
taking over management of an existing Ops Manager
with Platform Automation Toolkit:

- For more information about deploying Concourse with CredHub and UAA,
  see [Install Concourse for Platform Automation](https://docs.vmware.com/en/Concourse-for-VMware-Tanzu/7.0/vmware-tanzu-concourse/GUID-installation-install-platform-automation.html).
- For more information about deploying Platform Automation Toolkit
  with a new Ops Manager, see [Installing Ops Manager](./how-to-guides/installing-opsman.html).
- For more information about deploying Platform Automation Toolkit
  with an existing Ops Manager, see
  [Upgrading an existing Ops Manager](./how-to-guides/upgrade-existing-opsman.html).

